      • resolveThreshold

        protected static java.lang.Integer resolveThreshold(int maximum,
                                                    EvictionPolicyType type)
        Resolves the Eviction policy threshold (a.k.a. maximum) based on the EvictionPolicyType. For instance EvictionPolicyType.HEAP_PERCENTAGE does not support maximum/threshold since the settings are determined by the GemFire/Geode cache critical heap percentage and eviction heap percentage System property settings.
        Parameters:
        maximum - integer value specifying the configured Eviction threshold.
        type - EvictionPolicyType specifying the type of Eviction algorithm.
        Returns:
        a resolved value for the Eviction maximum/threshold.
        See Also:
        EvictionPolicyType
